data: {"candidates": [{"content": {"parts": [{"text": "**Seeking a Superior Punchline**\n\nI'm aiming for something truly excellent, surpassing the atom and pianist jokes. \"Better\" is the goal here – a clever setup, a surprising twist, and possibly more layered humor are the key ingredients. Norm's moth joke might be a good starting point.\n\n\n","thought": true}],"role": "model"},"index": 0}],"usageMetadata": {"promptTokenCount": 484,"totalTokenCount": 484,"promptTokensDetails": [{"modality": "TEXT","tokenCount": 484}],"serviceTier": "standard"},"modelVersion": "gemini-3-flash-preview","responseId": "OkUBas_hMOiu_PUPrL_U4AU"}

data: {"candidates": [{"content": {"parts": [{"text": "**Evaluating Joke Candidates**\n\nI've been evaluating several joke options. The \"Talking Dog\" concept feels strong: a compelling narrative with a simple twist. I've sketched a setup with a dog's incredible (and false) life story, culminating in its low price due to dishonesty. I also developed a bear and a rabbit scenario. The goal is to maximize setup, twist and punchline.\n\n\n","thought": true}],"role": "model"},"index": 0}],"usageMetadata": {"promptTokenCount": 484,"totalTokenCount": 484,"promptTokensDetails": [{"modality": "TEXT","tokenCount": 484}],"serviceTier": "standard"},"modelVersion": "gemini-3-flash-preview","responseId": "OkUBas_hMOiu_PUPrL_U4AU"}

